Python Inheritance:
1) Single Inheritance
   -> class Subclass(BaseClass):
2) Multiple 
   -> class Subclass(BaseClass1, BaseClass2, ...):
3) Multilevel
   -> class Subclass1(BaseClass1): and class Subclass2(Subclass1):
4) Hierarchical
   -> class Subclass1(BaseClass): and class Subclass2(BaseClass):
 
